Module instructions

Package fr.project.instructions.simple

Provides classes that represent simple java instructions
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Instruction
    An interface that represents any type of instruction of a .class file.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Field
    A class that allows to represent a simple field of a .class file.
    FieldInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write a field instruction of a .class file.
    FrameInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write a frame instruction of a .class file.
    IincInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write a increment instruction of a .class file.
    InnerClass
    A class that represents an inner class of a .class file.
    InstructionsCollector
    A class that allows to store a list of Instruction.
    IntInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write an int instruction of a .class file.
    InvokeDynamicInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write an invoke dynamic instruction of a .class file.
    JumpInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write a jump instruction of a .class file.
    LabelInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write a label instruction of a .class file.
    LdcInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write a ldc instruction of a .class file.
    LineNumberInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write a line number instruction of a .class file.
    LookupSwitchInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write a lookup switch instruction of a .class file.
    Method
    A class that represents a method of a .class file.
    MethodInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write a method instruction of a .class file.
    MultiANewArrayInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write a multi a new array instruction of a .class file.
    MyClass
    A class that represents a class of a .class file.
    NopInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write a zero instruction of a .class file.
    TableSwitchInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write a table switch instruction of a .class file.
    TryCatchBlock
    A class that allows to detect and write a try catch block instruction of a .class file.
    TryCatchBlockInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write a try catch block instruction of a .class file.
    TypeInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write a type instruction of a .class file.
    Utils
    A class that provides tools to write instruction in java bytecode.
    VarInstruction
    A class that allows to detect and write a variable instruction of a .class file.
